{
  "text": "Therefore, monoclonal antibodies against cardiac troponin-T with little or no cross-reactivity with its respective skeletal muscle isoforms have been evolved [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "28755936"
